@startuml gkg_deploy_dedicated
!include gkg_common.puml

title Deployment: GitLab Dedicated

' ===================================================================
' DEDICATED-SPECIFIC: ClickHouse Cloud per-tenant, control plane
' ===================================================================
database "**ClickHouse Cloud**\nCode + SDLC data lake\n(per-tenant instance)" as ch #d09191

rectangle "**Dedicated Control Plane**" as cp #F5F5F5 {
  component "Provisioning\n& Updates" as prov
}

' Data layer connections
sdlc_idx --> ch : TCP native (write)
code_idx --> ch : TCP native (write)
query_eng --> ch : TCP native (read, parameterized SQL)

' Control plane
prov --> module : deploy / update

note bottom of module
  **Provisioned:** One Orbit instance + ClickHouse Cloud
  database per tenant. Fully isolated.

  **Billing:** Same credit-based model as SaaS.

  **Updated:** Via Dedicated control plane,
  independent of monolith release cycle.
end note

@enduml
